## Step 6: LoadingButton Connection

```dart
LoadingButton(
  title: LocaleKeys.submit.tr(),
  cubit: context.read<SubmitCubit>(),
  onTap: () {
    if (!params.validateAndScroll()) return;
    final params = _vc.toParams();
    context.read<SubmitCubit>().submit(params);
  },
)
```

